		       News file for MMCK Checks
		       =========================

Revision 0.3.1-devel.1
----------------------

* Added CSS to HTML documentation.

* Added typed language support in library.

* Fixed wrong license notices.


Revision 0.3.1-devel.0
----------------------

* Removed some stale code and documentation.


Revision 0.3.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Changed library installation directory to:

     ${libdir}/chicken/$VERSION

  where $VERSION is the version number of the CHICKEN package.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.4
----------------------

* Fixed export list of WITH-RESULT.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.3
----------------------

* Added missing definition of values->list.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.2
----------------------

* Better exceptional conditions handling.

* Removed useless stuff from the distribution


Revision 0.2.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Renamed the project from MMUX CHICKEN Checks to MMCK Checks.

* Tweaking makefile.


Revision 0.1.0-devel.1
----------------------

* Makefile development.

* Changed handling of package version.

* BACKWARDS INCOMPATIBILITY Changed API of package version inspection.


Revision 0.1.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Initial development release.


